        <item>
            <title>廣汽傳祺 E9 PHEV MPV 到港展出，混能系統續航力可達 1442km</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/01/aion-e9-phev/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=aion-e9-phev</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/01/aion-e9-phev/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 07:00:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Aion]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[E9 PHEV]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[廣汽傳祺]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[廣汽埃安]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[廣汽集團]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1239643</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>廣汽集團旗下電動車品牌廣汽埃安（AION）今日宣傳品牌旗下最新的灣仔展廳正式啟用，同場亦展出了全新 2024 款廣汽傳祺 E9 PHEV 豪華 MPV。這款充電混能豪華 7 人 MPV 預計將於今年第四季正式發售。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239650" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/image-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/image-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/image.jpg 1269w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>廣汽傳祺 E9 外觀用上「醒獅前臉」設計，展現了豪華且現代的風格。車身長 5,212mm、闊 1,893mm、高 1,823mm，軸距 3,070mm。新車採用了流線型的設計，優雅線條中帶有動感，前臉設計具有很高的辨識度，搭配 LED 頭燈，增添了不少科技感。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239652" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2024e9phevgacmotori4-694x402.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="402" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2024e9phevgacmotori4-694x402.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2024e9phevgacmotori4.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>廣汽傳祺 E9 內籠設計方面，座椅安排為 2+2+3 形式，中排兩張電動冷暖大班椅具備按摩功能，手枕前端設有可調式觸控屏幕，座椅下方位置還有杯架、USB 充電位及英式三腳插頭，車內空間寬敞，乘坐舒適性極高。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239657" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/whatsapp202405311959-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/whatsapp202405311959-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/whatsapp202405311959.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239659" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_161059-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_161059-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_161059-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239660" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_160954-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_160954-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_160954-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239648" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/1400x0_1_q95_autohom-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/1400x0_1_q95_autohom-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/1400x0_1_q95_autohom.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在中控台和娛樂系統方面，廣汽傳祺 E9 配備了 15.6 吋頂置屏幕連影音娛樂系統，儀錶板設計則簡約而不失科技感，顯示清晰各項行車數據。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239658" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_161049-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_161049-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_161049-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>廣汽傳祺 E9 搭載充電混能系統，擁有一個 2 公升引擎、25.57kWh 容量電池，以及前驅電動馬達。系統總馬力可達 274kW（約 367 PS），峯值扭力可達 630Nm。加速方面，0-100km/h 加速只需 8.8 秒。混能系統提供的總續航裏數高達 1,442km，綜合耗油量 6.05L/100km。純電模式則可讓車輛行走 136km（CLTC）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239649" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/1400x0_1_q95_autohom-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/1400x0_1_q95_autohom-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/1400x0_1_q95_autohom-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>最在行車安全系統方面，廣汽傳祺 E9 也毫不遜色，配備了多種先進的安全技術，為駕駛者和乘客提供了全方位的保障。包括前方碰撞預警、車道偏離預警、倒車車側預警，開門預警等主動安全技術，讓行車更加安心。</p><p>廣汽傳祺 E9 預計在今年第四季正式登陸香港市場，售價待定。而在灣仔 AION 全新展廳除展出了 E9 之外，同場亦有 HYPER HT 同 AION Y PLUS 展出。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239661" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_1545021-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_1545021-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_1545021-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239662" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc02012-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc02012-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc02012-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/01/aion-e9-phev/life-tech/auto/">廣汽傳祺 E9 PHEV MPV 到港展出，混能系統續航力可達 1442km</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
