        <item>
            <title>長城歐拉 ORA 07 登陸香港　「一換一」售價 239,900 起</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/ora-07-hk/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ora-07-hk</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/ora-07-hk/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 12:15:36 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Ora]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[電動車]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1239588</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近年在香港中國品牌電動車選擇越來越多，最近長城汽車旗下的 ORA（歐拉）繼之前的 03 後，正式推出 ORA 07 四門跑房車系列，「一換一」售價由 239,900 起。今日這部超流線型 4 門純電轎跑車 ORA 07 就率先登陸將軍澳寶林 <span lang="EN-US">MCP CENTRAL </span>展出。小編就到現場同大家率先睇這部剛剛來港的新電動車。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239618" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_152846-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_152846-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_152846.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239619" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_152930-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_152930-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_152930.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span id="more-1239588"></span></p><p>ORA 07 本身在中國名為「閃電貓」，外觀和車廂設計也一貫品牌其他車款的圓潤風格，類似賓利 Continental GT，尺寸為 4,874 x 1,850 x 1,500mm，軸距則為 2,870mm。登陸香港的 ORA 07 有三個版本，包括標準前驅版本（續航距離 440 公里）、長續航前驅版本（續航距離 570 公里），以及四驅 GT 版本（續航距離 520 公里），三個版本的「一換一」售價分別為 HK$239,000 起、HK$269,000 起和 HK$329,000 起。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239636" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153949-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153949-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153949-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239620" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153544-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153544-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153544.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239621" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153549-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153549-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153549.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239622" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153606-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153606-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153606-rotated.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239623" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153626-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153626-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153626.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>ORA 07 採超流線型車身和無框車窗設計，提升視覺美感之餘，更將行車風阻系數降至 0.22cd，讓行車效能大大提高，每次充電後行駛距離也得到延長。</p><p>內籠設計同樣令人驚艷，車廂採用全球首次引入的空調紫外線殺菌燈，為駕駛者與乘客提供潔淨空氣。前後座位皆以仿真皮革包覆，搭配亮眼橙色內飾，既展現活力又不失優雅。擋風玻璃以及前座車窗採用減音材料製成，提供更寧靜的車廂環境。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239624" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153727-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153727-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153727.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239628" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153824-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153824-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153824.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239626" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153653-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153653-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153653-rotated.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239627" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_1537190-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_1537190-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_1537190.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239633" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_1035-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_1035-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_1035.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>ORA 07 配備了多項先進科技系統，包括自動調節進氣格柵，能夠根據外界氣温自動開合，確保摩打在最佳環境下運行。同時，車輛搭載四輪驅動系統，提供穩定的駕駛體驗。電池容量達 83 kWh，最大續航距離可達 520 公里，讓駕駛者無需頻繁充電即可輕鬆出行。動力方面，標準前驅版本和長續航前驅版本馬力有 204ps、扭力 340Nm，0 至 100 km/h 加速時間為 7.9 秒，而四驅 GT 版本則採用雙摩打四驅，馬力達到 408ps、扭力 680Nm，0 至 100km/h 加速時間為 4.3 秒。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239629" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153835-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153835-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153835.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239634" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_10242-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_10242-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_10242.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>行車安全方面，全車以 77.6% 高強度材質製作，並配有 L2 智能駕駛輔助系統，包括「ACC」主動式車距調節巡航系統及「ICC」智能巡航控制。車輛前方裝有行車鏡頭、12 個超聲波感應器和 2 個毫米波雷達，為駕駛者及乘客提供全方位的安全保障。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239631" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_10302-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_10302-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_10302.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239632" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_1023-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_1023-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_1023.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><strong>ORA 07 車款詳細規格</strong></p><ul><li>電池容量：83 kWh</li><li>最大續航距離：520 公里（WLTP combine）</li><li>最大功率：300 kW</li><li>最大扭力：680 Nm</li><li>車身尺寸：4,874 x 1,850 x 1,500 mm</li></ul><ul><li>價格（一換一意向價）：
<ul><li>ORA 07 Standard Range：HKD $239,900</li><li>ORA 07 Long Range：HKD $269,900</li><li>ORA AWD GT：HKD $329,800</li></ul></li></ul><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239599" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240531at-2-501x580.jpg" alt="" width="501" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240531at-2-501x580.jpg 501w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240531at-2-scaled.jpg 777w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 501px" /></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/06/onvo-l60-from-nio-ev/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">蔚來子品牌 ONVO 電動車，將於月中發表支援換電</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/25/polestar-phone-launched/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Polestar Phone 發表，暫時只對應 Polestar 4 電動車</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/07/made-in-china-kia-ev5-international-version/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">中國製 KIA EV5 電動車，國際版率先出口泰國澳洲</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/ora-07-hk/life-tech/auto/">長城歐拉 ORA 07 登陸香港　「一換一」售價 239,900 起</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
